pidgin-libnotify
------------------------------------------
This plugin adds a libnotify interface to pidgin, enabling popups much 
like guifications. It has some configuration options, to show popups 
when a buddy signs on, on new messages and on new conversations only.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-11
  gdk-pixbuf2-2.12.9-1
  glib2-2.14.6-1
  gtk2-x11-2.12.9-1
  libintl8-0.15-1
  libnotify-0.4.4-1
  libpurple-2.4.2-1
  pidgin-2.4.2-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf2.5-2.61-1
  automake1.9-1.9.6-2
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.3.10-1
  gawk-3.1.6-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  gettext-devel-0.15-1
  glib2-devel-2.14.6-1
  gnome-common-2.20.0-1
  libtool-2.2.2-2
  make-3.81-1
  pkg-config-0.21-1
  sed-4.1.5-2

Canonical website:
  http://gaim-libnotify.sourceforge.net/

Canonical download:
  http://sourceforge.net/projects/gaim-libnotify/files

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack pidgin-libnotify-0.13-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./pidgin-libnotify-0.13-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/pidgin-libnotify-0.13-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/pidgin-libnotify-0.13-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

